      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TINKER RAYS (2) turned in a fair 5th placed finish last time at Geelong over 400m (23.18). Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Rates on top in this line up. BENGAL BULLET (1) produced a modest effort most recently when eighth at Bendigo over 425m behind Aston Katy (25.73) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. One of the better hopes. KEY BEGONIA (7) has missed the frame at her last two but did run well three back when second (22.73) in a Grade 5 at this track. Well placed here and should do much better. FLYING BESSIE (5) is on a run of two minor placings and will be thereabouts again.",
